title: The Confessions of Arsene Lupin
creator: Maurice Leblanc
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Confessions of Arsene Lupin, by Maurice Leblanc. Read by Cathy Barratt. A collection of nine stories - or confessions - of the celebrated gentleman thief Arsene Lupin. (Summary by Cathy Barratt) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: adventure; fiction; mystery; gentleman thief
